                            New to the DRC? Start Here
                    

                Start the student registration process
            












                            Exam Proctoring Form for Instructors
                    

                Instructors fill out this form for students scheduled to take their exam at the DRC.
            












                            Request ASL Interpreters/CART Captionists
                    

                Fill out this form to request captioning/interpreters
            












                            Request Alternate Format
                    

                Complete this form to request textbooks and course materials in alternate text
            












                            Request Peer Note Taker
                    

                Students approved for the accommodation of peer note taker should complete this form to set up services
            












                            More DRC Resources
                    

                Check out DRC guides, referrals, and presentations
            



















 
